    "description": "Spice up your pasta bake with a sizzling Calabrian pork salume known as 'Nduja (\"en-doo-ya\"). For maximum flavour with little effort, add it to your rich, roasted aubergine & fennel sauce with gnocchi, then bake until golden. Delish!",
